---
import FeatureShowcase from '../react/FeatureShowcase';
---

<section class="py-24 bg-neutral-800 text-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 mb-4 bg-gold/20 border border-gold text-gold text-label rounded-full">
        Uzmanlık Alanlarımız
      </div>
      <h2 class="heading-section text-white">
        <span class="text-gold">Uçtan Uca </span>Çözümler
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Fuar standı, kongre ve tanıtım projelerinde tasarımdan üretime, kurulumdan teknik desteğe kadar tüm süreci tek elden yönetiyoruz.
      </p>
    </div>

    <FeatureShowcase client:load />
    
    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <a 
        href="/capabilities" 
        class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 bg-gold hover:bg-gold/80 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all group"
      >
        Detaylı İncele
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

